&lt;li&gt;Project Management experience (preferably in an external client-facing role)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data migration and/or conversion experience at a SaaS company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical skills (familiar with relational tables and databases)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
