&lt;p&gt;As a Sr. Account Executive, you should possess a strong blend of strategic thinking, leadership, and a results-oriented mindset. You should have a track record of successful sales management, particularly in sales to new customers, demonstrating their ability to meet or exceed sales targets. Your success as a member of the sales team will have a direct contribution to Bloomerang’s impact in the nonprofit industry.&lt;/p&gt;
